name: Ch._Empress_Sunwinds_Messenger_Chung-Chung_LaFlorin_III._Dotty
display_name: Ch. Empress Sunwinds Messenger Chung-Chung LaFlorin III. Dotty
content:
Ch. Empress Sunwinds Messenger Chung-Chung LaFlorin III. Dotty, or Dotty for short, was a pet voorpak belonging to the female Lady Deprovan.
Dotty was first mentioned in a mission terminal quest in the 2003 massively multiplayer online roleplaying game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided.
